    <div data-quickedit-entity-id="block_content/20" id="block-bandeauaccueil" class="contextual-region block-bandeauaccueil block block-block-content">
      
        <div data-contextual-id="block:block=bandeauaccueil:langcode=en|block_content:block_content=20:changed=1466018519&amp;langcode=en"></div>
        <div data-quickedit-field-id="block_content/20/body/en/full" class="field field-block-content--body field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden">
    <div class="field-items">
          <div class="field-item"><div class="img"><img alt="bandeau" data-entity-type="file" data-entity-uuid="9ba85eac-0c78-4c65-b819-255650008ff8" height="250" src="/sites/default/files/inline-images/residences-aines_0.jpg" width="250" /></div>
<h2 class="date">The rights and obligations of the tenants and owners of private seniors’ residences: the Québec Ombudsman’s report</h2>
<p>In a special report released on June 16, 2016, the Québec Ombudsman shed light on the difficulties tenants in private seniors’ residences experience in having their rights upheld when they have to face off against the owner in court.</p>
<p><a href="http://bit.ly/1UsWf3g" target="_blank" title="This link will open in a new window">For further information</a></p>
</div>
      </div>
</div>

  </div>

  </div>
</div>
          </div>
        
