          <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div data-contextual-id="block:block=faqaccueil_en:langcode=en|entity.view.edit_form:view=blocs_de_l_accueil:location=block&amp;name=blocs_de_l_accueil&amp;display_id=block_2&amp;langcode=en"></div>
